### Pengujian Titik Akhir API Manajemen Perusahaan (Tenant)
### PENTING: Ganti {{token}} dengan token JWT dari hasil login di test_auth.http

# 1. Membuat Profil Perusahaan Baru
# Akses: Hanya OWNER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/companies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJwYW5qYW5na2FzYUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzMyOTY0OTQsImV4cCI6MTc3MzM4Mjg5NH0.w7nD0k8LFevj1IJ1GHR3eHXca1fWQ5yQNjjkk8XXDDQ

{
  "name": "PT Maju Sejahtera",
  "address": "Jl. Jendral Sudirman No. 10, Jakarta Selatan",
  "taxNumber": "01.234.567.8-123.000"
}

###

